Tools for z-music.org project

$ zmusic download search 'keyword'                 -- download into current directory all mp3s found by keyword
$ zmusic play search 'keyword'                     -- play

$ zmusic download artist 'artist name'             -- download into current directory all mp3s of the artist
$ zmusic play artist 'artist name'                 -- play

$ zmusic download album 'artist name' 'album name' -- download into current directory all mp3s from the album
$ zmusic play album 'artist name' 'album name'     -- play

NOTE: artist name and album name are case sensivitive! The must be specified exatly as on the website.

Requirements:

perl
perl-lwp
wget
mplayer
